summary: Adds a teleporter to Riverwood(behind the saw mill) that will teleport you to the testing hall
descriptionHtml:
This is a very simple mod that adds a teleporter to Riverwood(behind the saw mill) and the Testing hall(QASmoke).

Added-2 re-spawning chests to the hall.
Food and Ingredient Chest-contains 250 of each food and Ingredient(might have missed a few)
Blacksmith Chest-contains 250 of each ore,ingot,leather,leather strip\'s,firewood(used in some mods)

Added 1-storage chest (safe to store items in)
I have also added a Candle Horn Chandelier to the testing hall near the blacksmith equipment to make the room a bit brighter 

I have moved nothing in the vanilla game so this mod is clean
author: HappyerbS
